00:23:27,329 --> 00:23:29,229
I can't take it anymore.

400
00:23:30,229 --> 00:23:33,929
Since today's our wedding anniversary.

401
00:23:33,929 --> 00:23:36,529
I thought it'd be a good time to get back together...

