00:23:38,729 --> 00:23:39,729
What I mean is...

403
00:23:40,729 --> 00:23:43,529
would you mind coming home now.

404
00:23:44,529 --> 00:23:45,829
Not quite yet!

405
00:23:45,829 --> 00:23:48,429
Saying something like this isn't going to get you off the hook.

406
00:23:52,429 --> 00:23:54,529
Am I getting a cold?

407
00:23:54,529 --> 00:23:56,229
I doubt it.

